Having trouble? Find quick solutions to common issues here.

## Quick Fixes

### Can't Log In

1. Check that your email address is correct
2. Make sure Caps Lock is off
3. Try "Forgot Password" to reset
4. Clear browser cookies and try again

### Report Not Generating

1. Check your internet connection
2. Refresh the page and check your dashboard
3. The report may still be processing â€” check for progress

### Chat Not Responding

1. Check if you've hit the rate limit (30/hour, 150/day)
2. Wait a moment and try again
3. Refresh the page

### Can't Share or Export

1. Make sure the report is fully complete
2. Try refreshing the page
3. Try a different browser

